      "content": "Wait, you're sure? I'm looking at the preliminary summary report from the automated scanner and it's just being really loud about the 'critical' tag. I don't see any evidence of an active exploit in the traffic logs yet. Are you 100% certain this isn't just a false positive or a low-impact vulnerability that we can just patch during the scheduled maintenance next week? A 6-hour blackout right now would cost us millions.",
